parameters: Villager: "Oh my, Umi-chan. It seems he's feeling better now."

Villager: "Oh, you're so polite. You're still recovering, so don't overdo
it."
Villager: "Oh my... hehehe, you're quite strong, aren't you?"
Villager: "Ah, oh Kru-san... this time... thank you very much."
Villager: "Ahh! It's wonderful to be alive!"

Villager: "Ah! Lord Kru! It's wonderful to be alive! Thank you so much for

Villager: "Oh... Are you feeling better now?"
Villager: "Umi-chan, that's great! You were really upset."
Villager: "Oh my... You've brought back quite a haul of game."
Villager: "Then... please take care of Umi-chan..."
Villager: "Mr. Kru... Thank you so much for saving our village..."
Villager: "Lord Kru... I'm truly glad you've returned safely."
Villager: "The view from here is the best, isn't it?"
Villager: "Lord Kru... The view from here is the best, isn't it?"
Villager: "Lord Kru, thank you for saving our village."

Kru (Alright... let's head to Mr. Iburu's house... It was to the east of
the village, if I remember correctly...)
Villager: "Big brother! Are you feeling better now?"
Kru: "Yes! Ah, thanks to you, I'm feeling much better."
Villager: "Oh! It's good to see you're feeling better!"
Villager: "Thanks to you, bro, we're having a feast tonight!"
Villager: "Please take care of this village..."
Villager: "Mr. Kru! I'm still alive, thanks to you!"
Villager: "Lord Kru! Thank you... Thank you so much!"
Villager: "I thought I was done for. Lord Kru... thank you very much."
Villager: "Oh, Lord Kru... this is the chieftain's house."
Villager: "I'm sorry... We just weren't good enough..."

Chancellor Shif: "Hahahaha!! Who's the terrible one here?! After all the
times we've been intimate, you dare betray me?!"

Chancellor Shif: "Do not call my name so casually! But... well, I suppose
you may... After all, we've shared the same woman over and over again!"

Chancellor Shif: "Whoa there... hold on... Are you sure you don't care what
happens to these people?"
Kru: "Damn it... You're such a cowardly man!"
Chancellor Shif: "The game is up. Accept your fate and surrender."
Chancellor Shif: "That depends on your attitude... Take them away!"
